_:N41a17a6aa81a44aba6b90197834797f8 <http://schema.org/description> "The Great Britain China Centre (GBCC) promotes mutual trust and understanding between the UK and China, building long-term connections between decision-makers in both countries. GBCC works for shared prosperity through dialogue and the promotion of rule of law, good governance and sustainable development. GBCC is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Foreign, Commonwealth & Development Office ." .
